author: Evan Sernoffsky
title: Honking S.F. cabbie beat up, robbed
text:
Photo: John O'Hara, Chronicle A Luxor cab driver was beat up and robbed Tuesday morning when a group of people became irritated that he was honking, police said. A Luxor cab driver was beat up and robbed Tuesday morning when a...
A crowd of people standing along Market Street in San Francisco got peeved at a cabbie for honking Tuesday morning, so they beat him up and robbed him, police said.
